Sentencas: A layered perovskite EnBaCo(2)O(5+delta) (EBCO) has been prepared by by a solid-state reaction, and evaluated as potential cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode

Sentencas: Structural characterizations are determined at room temperature using powder X-ray diffraction and transmission electron microscopy technique.
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode

Sentencas: The good fits to the XRD data by Rietveld refinement method are obtained in the orthorhombic space group (Pmmm).
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode

Sentencas: The lower average thermal expansion coefficient, 14.9 x 10(-6) degrees C-1 between 100 and 800 degrees C, indicates its better thermal expansion compatibility with conventional electrolytes, compared with the other cobalt-containing cathode materials.
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode

Sentencas: The high electrical conductivity and large oxygen nonstoichiometry at intermedia at temperatures suggest the effective charge transfer reactions including electron conduction and oxide-ion motion in cathode.
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode

Sentencas: As a result, a highly electrochemical activity towards the oxygen reduction reaction is achieved between 600 and 700 degrees C, as evidenced by low area-specific resistances, e.g. 0.14-0.5 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode

Sentencas: In addition, cathodic overpotential and oxygen reduction kinetics of the EBCO cathode have also been studied
Titulo: A Layered Perovskite EuBaCo2O5+δ for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathode
